(MRS HIGGINS the charlady enters.)
MRS_HIGGINS. Mornin' Mr. 'annay! 'ow yer keepin'? What a lovely morning this morning it is this morning. What about this 'ere heat wave! Never seen nothing like it. People droppin like --
(Pulls dust-sheet off ANNABELLA. Freezes. Screams a blood-curdling silent Munch-like scream.)
(Segues into deafening train whistle.)
(Train music.)

