!SCENE Eight: Edinburgh Station. Day.
SALESMAN_1. Wonder what won the two o'clock at Windsor.
SALESMAN_2. I'll get a paper.
SALESMAN_1. I'll go to the lavatory.
(They get up. Squeeze round each other.)
SALESMAN_1. Excuse me. Sorry. Sorry.
SALESMAN_2. Sorry. Sorry.
HANNAY. Sorry.
