PAPERBOY. Evenin paper! Latest news! Evenin paper! Latest --
SALESMAN_2. Evenin paper please?
PAPERBOY. Evening paper sir? Thankoo sir!
(gives him a paper)
SALESMAN_2. (gives him a penny) Thankoo.
PAPERBOY. Evenin paper! Latest news! Evenin paper! Latest --
