SALESMAN_1. All these sex dramas. Don't appeal to me! What won?
SALESMAN_2. What won what?
SALESMAN_1. The two O'clock at Windsor.
SALESMAN_2. Two O'clock at Windsor? (Turns paper over. They read the back. HANNAY peers at the front. ) Bachelor Boy.
SALESMAN_1. Good.
